flowchart TB
    s["provider.stream(request)"] --> pull["pull the FIRST event"]
    pull -->|ok| through["deliver + pass the rest through<br/>(mid-stream breaks are never retried)"]
    pull -->|throws| cls{"transient?<br/>408/409/425/429/5xx · IOException ·<br/>TransientProviderException"}
    cls -->|no: 401/404/...| fail["rethrow → error event"]
    cls -->|yes| budget{"attempts left?<br/>(maxRetries, default 2)"}
    budget -->|no| fail
    budget -->|yes| sleep["backoff: 250 ms · ×2 · cap 8 s<br/>+ 20% jitter (cancel-aware)"]
    sleep --> pull
